These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: cola, sprite, juice, mirinda
Pet: hedgehog, bird, hamster, guinea-pig
1. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left of Beverage:juice##1
2. Beverage:cola is on the left of Pet:bird##1
3. Beverage:mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:hamster is on the left or right of Pet:guinea-pig##3
5. Beverage:cola is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | cola | sprite | mirinda | juice |
| Pet        | hedgehog | bird   | guinea-pig | hamster    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: adventure, martial-arts, animation, action
Nationality: canadian, polish, italian, australian
1. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the left of Movie-Genre:action##1
2. Nationality:canadian is on the left of Nationality:italian##1
3. Nationality:italian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:canadian == Movie-Genre:adventure##1
5. Nationality:polish is on the right of Nationality:italian##1
6. Nationality:canadian == Movie-Genre:adventure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | adventure  | martial-arts  | action |
| Nationality   | australian    | canadian | italian | polish    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: peas, raspberry, artichoke, lime
Movie-Genre: zombie, thriller, horror, martial-arts
1. Food:lime is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:martial-arts##3
2. Food:artichoke is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the left or right of Food:raspberry##3
4. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the right of Movie-Genre:horror##1
5. Movie-Genre:zombie is in an odd position##4
6. Food:raspberry is on the right of Food:artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | lime | artichoke | raspberry    | peas      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror        | martial-arts     | zombie | thriller |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: chess, camping, traveling, rock-climbing
Music-Genre: soul, funk, rock, trance
1. Hobby:camping is between Music-Genre:soul and Music-Genre:trance##2
2. Hobby:rock-climbing is on the left of Hobby:chess##1
3. Music-Genre:rock is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:funk is on the left of Music-Genre:trance##1
5. Music-Genre:funk is on the right of Hobby:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | chess | camping | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | soul   | funk    | trance  |

