.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: electronic, house, soul, dubstep
Nationality: canadian, thai, malaysian, japanese
1. Music-Genre:soul is on the right of Nationality:japanese##1
2. Nationality:thai == Music-Genre:dubstep##1
3. Nationality:malaysian is on the right of Music-Genre:electronic##1
4. Music-Genre:house is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:soul is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house  | electronic    | soul   | dubstep       |
| Nationality   | canadian | japanese | malaysian | thai |

