2. Music-Genre:ambient is on the right of Beverage:milk##1
3. Music-Genre:r&b is between Music-Genre:ambient and Beverage:7up##2
4. Beverage:milk is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:r&b is on the left or right of Music-Genre:ambient##3
6. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left or right of Music-Genre:reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | 7up   | milk | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | reggae | r&b        | ambient    |

