4. Food:onion is on the left of Food:papaya##1
5. Food:papaya is on the right of Beverage:iced-tea##1
6. Food:onion is in an even position##4
7. Food:radish == Beverage:hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | iced-tea    | tea       | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | garlic  | onion | papaya | radish  |

